'''Twi'janii''' was a [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] ritual extending hospitality to respected guests, who were considered honorary members of the clan. When twi'janii was invoked, the [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] people of [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]] were obliged to offer their guests sustenance and entertainment.

==Behind the scenes==
In its one mention in [[Star Wars (1998) 21|''Star Wars'' (1998) 21]], the final I is left off the word, spelling it '''twi'jani'''.

